settings.description: After Mario gets through Cloud Land 1, he finds an airship and must steal the treasure! Don't die! Cloud Land 2 is next.
This level have a secret exit,it's nothing special but it has a 3-up moon and is the way to collect the E-coin,enjoy
Wiggler ahoy! seems these caterpillars and butterflies are all around this chilly place!
The next level is the wendy's castle,enjoy.
Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. This is the airship section, and the transition to desert land.
Mario goes through the starting area of Bowser's Airship and must defeat boom boom. Bowsers airship 2 is next.
We finish the first world,the next one is in the desert.
I think I'm getting better at making levels.
oopsies... i forgot to add a description to the last level.
